{"name":"Broadsword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A wide-bladed sword designed for powerful cutting and thrusting attacks. Effective in one hand, the broadsword rewards aggressive fighters who press their advantage.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee 2d4, Keen, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee 2d4, Keen, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Falchion","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-falchion-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A single-edged curved blade weighted toward the tip for devastating cleaving strikes. Favored by warriors who rely on raw power to overwhelm their opponents.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d8, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d10, Disarm, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d10, Disarm, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Your powerful blows count as critical hits for the purpose of triggering on-crit effects and resistances.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your powerful blows count as critical hits for the purpose of triggering on-crit effects and resistances."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Greatsword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-guard-glowing-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The quintessential two-handed blade, a greatsword combines reach, power, and precision into a single imposing weapon. Its keen edge and heavy construction let it stagger foes and carve through armor.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Keen, Stagger</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Keen, Stagger — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d12 damage instead of 2d10.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":50,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d12 damage instead of 2d10."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Ikakalaka","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-stone.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy chopping sword of island origin, with a broad serrated blade that both deflects incoming blows and punishes enemies who close in. Its weight makes it unforgiving but powerful.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Deflect, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Deflect, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Deflect now works against ranged attacks. Knockback and Trip effects from this weapon benefit from the Keen property.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":30,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Deflect now works against ranged attacks. Knockback and Trip effects from this weapon benefit from the Keen property."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Katana","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/katana-ornate-orange.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A gracefully curved blade forged for speed and precision. Equally effective in one or two hands, the katana rewards disciplined fighters who blend offense with defense.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Versatile d8, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Versatile d8, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Add your proficiency bonus to one-handed Deflect rolls. Two-handed Deflect uses 2d10.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Add your proficiency bonus to one-handed Deflect rolls. Two-handed Deflect uses 2d10."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Khopesh","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-curved-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An ancient sickle-sword with an inner hook ideal for disarming and tripping opponents. Light and effective, the khopesh punishes enemies who rely on heavy weapons or sure footing.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee 2d4, Disarm, Keen, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee 2d4, Disarm, Keen, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft and the target has disadvantage on Strength saving throws until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft and the target has disadvantage on Strength saving throws until the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Longsword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-guard-silver-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The classic knight's blade, balanced for versatile use in one or two hands. Reliable in all situations, the longsword rewards technical fighters who excel at controlling their opponents.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10, Balanced, Disarm</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10, Balanced, Disarm — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded one-handed, and 18-20 when wielded two-handed.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded one-handed, and 18-20 when wielded two-handed."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Montante","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-silver.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive Iberian two-handed sword used to hold off multiple attackers. Its reach and balance allow a trained fighter to protect companions by denying approach.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6, Balanced — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction you enter a protective stance. All attacks made against your allies within your reach have disadvantage until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As a reaction you enter a protective stance. All attacks made against your allies within your reach have disadvantage until the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Odachi","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-ornate-gold.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An extraordinarily long Japanese field sword built for sweeping strikes against multiple enemies. Masters use its length to chain attacks across the battlefield with devastating efficiency.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Deflect, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d8, Deflect, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you attack a creature different from the last creature you attacked this turn, you deal an extra damage die on a hit.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":50,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you attack a creature different from the last creature you attacked this turn, you deal an extra damage die on a hit."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Scimitar","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/scimitar-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A curved cavalry blade designed to deliver slashing blows on the move. The scimitar rewards aggressive fighters who keep their momentum, hitting harder after closing distance.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Deflect, Riposte</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Deflect, Riposte — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you travel 20 ft or more before attacking (including while mounted), your next attack with this weapon deals an extra d8 damage.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you travel 20 ft or more before attacking (including while mounted), your next attack with this weapon deals an extra d8 damage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Short Glaive","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-silver.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact polearm-style blade combining a glaive's cutting edge with a sword's maneuverability. The short glaive enables mobile fighters to brace against charges, lunge forward, and disengage without opening themselves to counterattack.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 2d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 3d4, Balanced, Brace, Lunge</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee 3d4, Balanced, Brace, Lunge — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you take the Dash action, you do not provoke opportunity attacks and may make one attack at any point during your movement.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":3,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you take the Dash action, you do not provoke opportunity attacks and may make one attack at any point during your movement."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Sword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-worn-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy, wide-bladed two-handed sword built to stagger armored opponents and cleave through large enemies. Brutal and reliable, it is the weapon of front-line soldiers who need guaranteed stopping power.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Stagger</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Stagger — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded two-handed. Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d8 (or 2d10 two-handed) instead of d12 (or 2d8 two-handed).</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":30,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Combat Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Critical hit range becomes 19-20 when wielded two-handed. Against Large or larger creatures, this weapon deals 2d8 (or 2d10 two-handed) instead of d12 (or 2d8 two-handed)."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Grapple Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy mechanized crossbow that fires a grapple bolt trailing a strong cable. Beyond dealing damage, it can entangle, trip, and restrain targets — or pull them toward the user.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6+4 (80/320), Reload bonus, Clockwork, Entangle, Keen, Punch, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d6+4 (80/320), Reload bonus, Clockwork, Entangle, Keen, Punch, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Targets have disadvantage on ability checks to resist the Entangle pull. You may choose to fire the grapple bolt without dealing damage.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":175,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":13,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":"4"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":80,"long":320,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Targets have disadvantage on ability checks to resist the Entangle pull. You may choose to fire the grapple bolt without dealing damage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hand Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact one-handed crossbow that fires with surprising force at close range. Its clockwork reload mechanism and hipshot capability make it a favorite for mobile skirmishers and ambushers.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d4 (30/120), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d6+2 (30/120), Reload free, Hipshot, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d6+2 (30/120), Reload free, Hipshot, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You can reload this crossbow one-handed. If you have not used your Attack action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"2"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can reload this crossbow one-handed. If you have not used your Attack action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Heavy Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A powerful siege-weight crossbow that punches through armor and knocks enemies off their feet. Skilled users can react to enemies trying to close or escape, turning the weapon into a battlefield deterrent.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (100/400), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10+4 (100/400), Reload bonus, Keen, Puncture, Sighted, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d10+4 (100/400), Reload bonus, Keen, Puncture, Sighted, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":50,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":8,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"4"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":100,"long":400,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hidden Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A tiny spring-loaded crossbow affixed to the wrist or forearm, concealed beneath a sleeve or glove. It fires with a flick of the wrist, ideal for assassins and spies who need a deniable ranged option at close range.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4 (20/60), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4+1 (20/60), Reload object interaction, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Keen, Slip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged d4+1 (20/60), Reload object interaction, Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Keen, Slip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you miss an attack with this weapon, you may use your reaction to make another attack against the same target.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":150,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"1"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you miss an attack with this weapon, you may use your reaction to make another attack against the same target."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Light Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A reliable two-handed crossbow balancing rate of fire and range. Sighted and steady, it suits disciplined marksmen who fire from prepared positions and punish enemies who try to close the distance.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8+3 (80/320), Reload reaction, Keen, Punch, Steady, Sighted</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d8+3 (80/320), Reload reaction, Keen, Punch, Steady, Sighted — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"3"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":80,"long":320,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As a reaction, you may make an attack against a creature that enters or leaves a space within 10 ft of you."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Mauler","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A short-ranged multi-bolt crossbow that fires a spread of bolts in a tight pattern. At close range it is devastating, shredding through flesh and punching through light armor with every volley.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (20/80), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 3d4+3 (20/80), Reload bonus, Hipshot, Keen, Puncture</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 3d4+3 (20/80), Reload bonus, Hipshot, Keen, Puncture — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>The Puncture property now activates when any individual die shows a 3 or 4, in addition to its normal triggers.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":100,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":3,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"3"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":80,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"The Puncture property now activates when any individual die shows a 3 or 4, in addition to its normal triggers."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Portable Ballista","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-heavy-ornate.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A man-portable siege weapon that fires massive bolts capable of pinning targets to terrain and restraining entire groups. Slow to load but catastrophically powerful, it dominates open ground.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged d8 (150/600), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d6+5 (150/600), Reload attack, Entangle, Keen, Knockback, Punch, Puncture, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d6+5 (150/600), Reload attack, Entangle, Keen, Knockback, Punch, Puncture, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Entangle also applies the restrained condition and pins the target to the terrain until freed.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":500,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":15,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":150,"long":600,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"A successful Entangle also applies the restrained condition and pins the target to the terrain until freed."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Repeating Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A magazine-fed crossbow that fires repeatedly without manual reloading. In trained hands it becomes a weapon of sustained fire superiority — at the cost of the user's movement.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (80/320), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Reload free, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d6 (80/320), Reload free, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you take the Attack action, you may make one additional attack as a bonus action. If you do, your speed becomes 0 until the start of your next turn.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":150,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":80,"long":320,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you take the Attack action, you may make one additional attack as a bonus action. If you do, your speed becomes 0 until the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Spinner","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/crossbows/crossbow-simple-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A clockwork rotary crossbow that fires razor discs rather than bolts. On full auto it can hit multiple nearby targets with a single trigger pull, making it ideal for crowd control.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged d4 (30/120), Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (30/120), Reload free, Clockwork, Disarm, Keen, Steady</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d4 (30/120), Reload free, Clockwork, Disarm, Keen, Steady — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>As an action, choose a number of targets up to your Intelligence modifier (minimum 1) each within 10 ft of the first target. Make a single attack roll against all of them, dealing damage to each you hit.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":100,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Crossbows","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action, choose a number of targets up to your Intelligence modifier (minimum 1) each within 10 ft of the first target. Make a single attack roll against all of them, dealing damage to each you hit."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Cutlass","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/scimitar-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A short, slightly curved naval blade built for close-quarters fighting. Equally at home on a ship deck or a city street, the cutlass rewards fighters who press relentlessly forward.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Deflect, Punch</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Deflect, Punch — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a critical hit or reduce a target to 0 HP, you may make an extra attack against a different creature within 5 ft. This can repeat if that attack also crits or reduces to 0 HP."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Dagger","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/dagger-straight-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The universal sidearm of adventurers everywhere. Concealable, throwable, and deadly in skilled hands, the dagger is as much a tool as a weapon — and masters make it terrifyingly effective.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Balanced, Conceal</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60), Balanced, Conceal — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You may make one additional attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You may make one additional attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Estoc","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-guard-silver-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long, stiff thrusting sword built to punch through plate armor and chainmail. The estoc has no cutting edge — only a rigid triangular or square blade that concentrates force on a needle point.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Brace, Punch, Wound</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Brace, Punch, Wound — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If you have not used your Attack action or held action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you have not used your Attack action or held action this turn, you may make one attack with this weapon as a bonus action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Kukri","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-curved-teal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A forward-curving Nepalese blade that chops as well as it slices. Throwable and light, the kukri excels at hamstringing enemies and leaving them unable to flee or fight effectively.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/40), Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (40/80), Keen, Trip</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (40/80), Keen, Trip — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft. The target must make a Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns to end the effect.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":80,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"A successful Trip reduces the target's speed by 10 ft. The target must make a Constitution saving throw at the end of each of its turns to end the effect."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Rapier","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/rapier-gold-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The weapon of choice for duelists and swashbucklers. Long, slender, and supremely precise, the rapier rewards fighters who commit fully to its use — punishing armor and keeping the blade in constant motion.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Puncture, Riposte</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Puncture, Riposte — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>If wielding only a rapier (no shield or other weapon), add d4 to your damage rolls. If dual wielding with a Light weapon, gain +1 to AC from weapon deflection.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If wielding only a rapier (no shield or other weapon), add d4 to your damage rolls. If dual wielding with a Light weapon, gain +1 to AC from weapon deflection."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Saber","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-guard-silver-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A curved cavalry sword as elegant as it is deadly. The saber's slight flex and razor edge let it turn aside attacks and deliver lightning counterstrikes — masters who dual wield them become engines of relentless offense.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d6, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Deflect, Keen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Deflect, Keen — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>Add d4 to Deflect rolls. While wielding two sabers, when you reduce an enemy to 0 HP you regain your reaction immediately.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":35,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Add d4 to Deflect rolls. While wielding two sabers, when you reduce an enemy to 0 HP you regain your reaction immediately."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Sai","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/dagger-straight-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A pronged iron weapon designed to catch and disarm blades. Small enough to conceal, the sai turns defense into offense — a miss against the sai's wielder may cost the attacker their own weapon.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Piercing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Conceal, Deflect, Nimble</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Conceal, Deflect, Nimble — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>You gain +1 to AC while wielding this weapon. When an enemy misses you with a melee attack, they must succeed on a Strength or Dexterity saving throw or drop their weapon.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You gain +1 to AC while wielding this weapon. When an enemy misses you with a melee attack, they must succeed on a Strength or Dexterity saving throw or drop their weapon."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Shortsword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-short.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact, well-balanced blade suited to close quarters and ambush fighting. Mastered, the shortsword's balance becomes an active combat tool — advantage lets the weapon truly shine.</p><h3>Training</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Level</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Slashing</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Balanced</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6, Balanced — all bonuses apply</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master Perk</strong></td><td>The Balanced property now also applies to attackers targeting you. When you have advantage on an attack roll, roll your damage dice and Balanced dice twice and use the better result.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Dueling Blades","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"The Balanced property now also applies to attackers targeting you. When you have advantage on an attack roll, roll your damage dice and Balanced dice twice and use the better result."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
